summary: ...OCTAVE HOLDING STEADY WHILE HEADING EAST-SOUTHEASTWARD... As of 2:00 AM PDT Tue Oct 07 the center of Octave was located near 15.8, -119.5 with movement ESE at 7 mph. The minimum central pressure was 998 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
